{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"I want to talk to you about,"},{"time":3561,"text":"or share with you, a\nbreakthrough new approach"},{"time":7122,"text":"for managing items of\ninventory inside of a warehouse."},{"time":10464,"text":"We're talking about a pick,\npack and ship setting here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":13022,"text":"So as a hint,"},{"time":15845,"text":"this solution involves\nhundreds of mobile robots,"},{"time":19998,"text":"sometimes thousands\nof mobile robots,"},{"time":22422,"text":"moving around a warehouse.\nAnd I'll get to the solution."},{"time":25020,"text":"But for a moment, just think"},{"time":26240,"text":"about the last time that\nyou ordered something online."},{"time":28766,"text":"You were sitting\non your couch"},{"time":30830,"text":"and you decided that you\nabsolutely had to have this red t-shirt."},{"time":34890,"text":"So — click! — you put it\ninto your shopping cart."},{"time":37186,"text":"And then you decided\nthat green pair of pants"},{"time":39084,"text":"looks pretty good too — click!"},{"time":40982,"text":"And maybe a blue\npair of shoes — click!"},{"time":42882,"text":"So at this point you've\nassembled your order."},{"time":44932,"text":"You didn't stop to think \nfor a moment that"},{"time":46700,"text":"that might not be a great outfit."},{"time":48468,"text":"But you hit\n\"submit order.\""},{"time":50238,"text":"And two days later, this package\nshows up on your doorstep."},{"time":54412,"text":"And you open the box and you're\nlike, wow, there's my goo."}]},{"cues":[{"time":57366,"text":"Did you ever stop to think about\nhow those items of inventory"},{"time":60327,"text":"actually found their way inside\nthat box in the warehouse?"},{"time":64540,"text":"So I'm here to tell you \nit's that guy right there."},{"time":68358,"text":"So deep in the\nmiddle of that picture,"},{"time":71978,"text":"you see a classic\npick-pack worker"},{"time":74493,"text":"in a distribution or\norder fulfillments setting."},{"time":77718,"text":"Classically these pick workers will \nspend 60 or 70 percent of their day"},{"time":81600,"text":"wandering around\nthe warehouse."},{"time":83512,"text":"They'll often walk\nas much as 5 or 10 miles"},{"time":86223,"text":"in pursuit of\nthose items of inventory."},{"time":88884,"text":"Not only is this an\nunproductive way to fill orders,"},{"time":93305,"text":"it also turns out to be an\nunfulfilling way to fill orders."}]},{"cues":[{"time":97362,"text":"So let me tell you where I\nfirst bumped into this problem."},{"time":100993,"text":"I was out in the Bay area \nin '99, 2000, the dot com boom."},{"time":105047,"text":"I worked for a fabulously\nspectacular flame-out called Webvan."},{"time":109109,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":110930,"text":"This company raised hundreds of\nmillions of dollars with the notion that"},{"time":113660,"text":"we will deliver\ngrocery orders online."},{"time":116442,"text":"And it really came down to the fact\nthat we couldn't do it cost effectively."},{"time":120615,"text":"Turns out e-commerce was something\nthat was very hard and very costly."},{"time":124577,"text":"In this particular instance we were trying\nto assemble 30 items of inventory"},{"time":128828,"text":"into a few totes, onto a van\nto deliver to the home."},{"time":132800,"text":"And when you think about it,\nit was costing us 30 dollars."},{"time":136600,"text":"Imagine, we had an\n89¢ can of soup"},{"time":139686,"text":"that was costing us one dollar to\npick and pack into that tote."},{"time":143362,"text":"And that's before we actually\ntried to deliver it to the home."}]},{"cues":[{"time":146570,"text":"So long story short,\nduring my one year at Webvan,"},{"time":149357,"text":"what I realized by talking to \nall the material-handling providers"},{"time":152593,"text":"was that there was no solution designed\nspecifically to solve each base picking."},{"time":157231,"text":"Red item, green, blue, getting\nthose three things in a box."},{"time":161254,"text":"So we said, there's just\ngot to be a better way to do this."},{"time":164239,"text":"Existing material handling\nwas set up to pump"},{"time":166766,"text":"pallets and cases of\ngoo to retail stores."}]},{"cues":[{"time":170533,"text":"Of course Webvan went out of business,\nand about a year and a half later,"},{"time":174330,"text":"I was still noodling on this problem.\nIt was still nagging at me."},{"time":177910,"text":"And I started\nthinking about it again."},{"time":179778,"text":"And I said, let me just focus briefly\non what I wanted as a pick worker,"},{"time":184905,"text":"or my vision for\nhow it should work."},{"time":187236,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":188650,"text":"I said, let's focus\non the problem."},{"time":190572,"text":"I have an order here and what\nI want to do is I want to put"},{"time":194427,"text":"red, green and blue\nin this box right here."},{"time":196647,"text":"What I need is a system where I put out\nmy hand and — poof! —"},{"time":199499,"text":"the product shows up \nand I pack it into the order,"},{"time":202022,"text":"and now we're thinking,"},{"time":203715,"text":"this would be a very operator-centric\napproach to solving the problem."},{"time":207729,"text":"This is what I need. What technology\nis available to solve this problem?"},{"time":211956,"text":"But as you can see, orders can come\nand go, products can come and go."},{"time":215897,"text":"It allows us to focus on making the\npick worker the center of the problem,"},{"time":220580,"text":"and providing them the tools to make\nthem as productive as possible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":225204,"text":"So how did I\narrive at this notion?"},{"time":227304,"text":"Well, actually it came from\na brainstorming exercise,"},{"time":230837,"text":"probably a technique\nthat many of you use,"},{"time":233677,"text":"It's this notion of\ntesting your ideas."},{"time":235833,"text":"Take a blank sheet, of course,"},{"time":237563,"text":"but then test your ideas\nat the limits — infinity, zero."},{"time":241593,"text":"In this particular case, we\nchallenged ourselves with the idea:"},{"time":244775,"text":"What if we had to build a\ndistribution center in China,"},{"time":247751,"text":"where it's a very,\nvery low-cost market?"},{"time":250365,"text":"And say, labor is cheap,\nland is cheap."},{"time":253578,"text":"And we said specifically,"},{"time":255224,"text":"\"What if it was zero dollars\nan hour for direct labor"},{"time":258230,"text":"and we could build a million-\nsquare-foot distribution center?\""},{"time":260946,"text":"So naturally that\nled to ideas that said,"},{"time":263021,"text":"\"Let's put lots of people\nin the warehouse.\""},{"time":264829,"text":"And I said, \"Hold on,\nzero dollars per hour,"},{"time":267374,"text":"what I would do is 'hire'"},{"time":270231,"text":"10,000 workers to come to the\nwarehouse every morning at 8 a.m.,"},{"time":274358,"text":"walk into the warehouse and\npick up one item of inventory"},{"time":277477,"text":"and then just stand there."},{"time":279210,"text":"So you hold Captain Crunch,\nyou hold the Mountain Dew,"},{"time":281749,"text":"you hold the Diet Coke."},{"time":283172,"text":"If I need it, I'll call you,\notherwise just stand there."},{"time":285428,"text":"But when I need Diet Coke and I call it,\nyou guys talk amongst yourselves."},{"time":288815,"text":"Diet Coke walks up to the front —\npick it, put it in the tote, away it goes.\""},{"time":292936,"text":"Wow, what if the products\ncould walk and talk on their own?"},{"time":297588,"text":"That's a very interesting,\nvery powerful way"},{"time":299926,"text":"that we could potentially\norganize this warehouse."}]},{"cues":[{"time":302520,"text":"So of course,\nlabor isn't free,"},{"time":304868,"text":"on that practical\nversus awesome spectrum."},{"time":308176,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":309866,"text":"So we said mobile shelving —\nWe'll put them on mobile shelving."},{"time":312983,"text":"We'll use mobile robots and\nwe'll move the inventory around."},{"time":317776,"text":"And so we got underway on that and\nthen I'm sitting on my couch in 2008."},{"time":322194,"text":"Did any of you see the Beijing\nOlympics, the opening ceremonies?"},{"time":326013,"text":"I about fell out of my\ncouch when I saw this."},{"time":329054,"text":"I'm like, that was the idea!"},{"time":330527,"text":"(Laughter and Applause)"},{"time":335026,"text":"We'll put thousands of people on\nthe warehouse floor, the stadium floor."},{"time":338917,"text":"But interestingly enough, this\nactually relates to the idea"},{"time":342952,"text":"in that these guys were creating some\nincredibly powerful, impressive digital art,"},{"time":348364,"text":"all without computers,\nI'm told,"},{"time":350440,"text":"it was all peer-to-peer\ncoordination and communication."},{"time":352886,"text":"You stand up,\nI'll squat down."},{"time":354462,"text":"And they made\nsome fabulous art."},{"time":356107,"text":"It speaks to the\npower of emergence"},{"time":358795,"text":"in systems when you let things\nstart to talk with each other."},{"time":362763,"text":"So that was a little\nbit of the journey."}]},{"cues":[{"time":366541,"text":"So of course, now what became\nthe practical reality of this idea?"},{"time":370579,"text":"Here is a warehouse."},{"time":372385,"text":"It's a pick, pack and ship center\nthat has about 10,000 different SKUs."},{"time":376161,"text":"We'll call them red pens,\ngreen pens, yellow Post-It Notes."},{"time":380298,"text":"We send the little orange robots\nout to pick up the blue shelving pods."},{"time":383677,"text":"And we deliver them\nto the side of the building."},{"time":385845,"text":"So all the pick workers now\nget to stay on the perimeter."},{"time":388981,"text":"And the game here is\nto pick up the shelves,"},{"time":391323,"text":"take them down the highway and\ndeliver them straight to the pick worker."},{"time":394647,"text":"This pick worker's life\nis completely different."},{"time":396784,"text":"Rather than wandering around\nthe warehouse, she gets to stay still"},{"time":400201,"text":"in a pick station like this"},{"time":401789,"text":"and every product in the\nbuilding can now come to her."}]},{"cues":[{"time":405787,"text":"So the process\nis very productive."},{"time":409065,"text":"Reach in, pick an item,\nscan the bar code, pack it out."},{"time":413260,"text":"By the time\nyou turn around,"},{"time":414909,"text":"there's another product there\nready to be picked and packed."},{"time":417948,"text":"So what we've done is take\nout all of the non-value added"},{"time":420958,"text":"walking, searching,\nwasting, waited time,"},{"time":423642,"text":"and we've developed a very \nhigh-fidelity way to pick these orders,"},{"time":427920,"text":"where you point at it with\na laser, scan the UPC barcode,"},{"time":432084,"text":"and then indicate with a light\nwhich box it needs to go into."},{"time":435278,"text":"So more productive, more\naccurate and, it turns out,"},{"time":438764,"text":"it's a more interesting office\nenvironment for these pick workers."},{"time":443070,"text":"They actually complete\nthe whole order."},{"time":445507,"text":"So they do red, green and blue,\nnot just a part of the order."},{"time":448034,"text":"And they feel a little bit more\nin control of their environment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":451648,"text":"So the side effects\nof this approach"},{"time":454846,"text":"are what really surprised us."},{"time":456414,"text":"We knew it was going \nto be more productive."},{"time":457992,"text":"But we didn't realize just how\npervasive this way of thinking"},{"time":462062,"text":"extended to other\nfunctions in the warehouse."},{"time":467292,"text":"But what effectively this approach\nis doing inside of the DC"},{"time":472124,"text":"is turning it into a massively\nparallel processing engine."},{"time":476588,"text":"So this is again a\ncross-fertilization of ideas."},{"time":479211,"text":"Here's a warehouse\nand we're thinking about"},{"time":481150,"text":"parallel processing\nsupercomputer architectures."},{"time":484669,"text":"The notion here is that you have"},{"time":487066,"text":"10 workers on \nthe right side of the screen"},{"time":489863,"text":"that are now all independent\nautonomous pick workers."},{"time":494111,"text":"If the worker in station three decides\nto leave and go to the bathroom,"},{"time":498015,"text":"it has no impact on the\nproductivity of the other nine workers."},{"time":501499,"text":"Contrast that, for a moment, with the\ntraditional method of using a conveyor."},{"time":505869,"text":"When one person\npasses the order to you,"},{"time":507928,"text":"you put something in\nand pass it downstream."},{"time":510427,"text":"Everyone has to be in place\nfor that serial process to work."},{"time":513544,"text":"This becomes a more robust\nway to think about the warehouse."}]},{"cues":[{"time":516721,"text":"And then underneath the hoods gets\ninteresting in that we're tracking"},{"time":521265,"text":"the popularity\nof the products."},{"time":523003,"text":"And we're using dynamic\nand adaptive algorithms"},{"time":525827,"text":"to tune the floor\nof the warehouse."},{"time":530281,"text":"So what you see here potentially\nthe week leading up to Valentine's Day."},{"time":535165,"text":"All that pink chalky candy has\nmoved to the front of the building"},{"time":539008,"text":"and is now being picked into a\nlot of orders in those pick stations."},{"time":542901,"text":"Come in two days after Valentine's Day,\nand that candy, the leftover candy,"},{"time":547064,"text":"has all drifted to the\nback of the warehouse"},{"time":549337,"text":"and is occupying the cooler\nzone on the thermal map there."},{"time":553630,"text":"One other side effect of this\napproach using the parallel processing"},{"time":557113,"text":"is these things can\nscale to ginormous."},{"time":560108,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":561635,"text":"So whether you're doing\ntwo pick stations, 20 pick stations,"},{"time":564369,"text":"or 200 pick stations, the\npath planning algorithms"},{"time":567642,"text":"and all of the inventory\nalgorithms just work."},{"time":570185,"text":"In this example you\nsee that the inventory"},{"time":574541,"text":"has now occupied all the\nperimeter of the building"},{"time":576867,"text":"because that's where\nthe pick stations were."},{"time":579213,"text":"They sorted it\nout for themselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":581231,"text":"So I'll conclude with\njust one final video"},{"time":583518,"text":"that shows how\nthis comes to bear"},{"time":586502,"text":"on the pick worker's actual\nday in the life of."},{"time":590096,"text":"So as we mentioned, the process is\nto move inventory along the highway"},{"time":594432,"text":"and then find your way\ninto these pick stations."},{"time":597084,"text":"And our software in the background"},{"time":599555,"text":"understands what's going on \nin each station,"},{"time":602306,"text":"we direct the pods\nacross the highway"},{"time":604917,"text":"and we're attempting to\nget into a queuing system"},{"time":607631,"text":"to present the work\nto the pick worker."},{"time":610515,"text":"What's interesting is we can even\nadapt the speed of the pick workers."},{"time":613760,"text":"The faster pickers get more pods\nand the slower pickers get few."},{"time":617686,"text":"But this pick worker now is\nliterally having that experience"},{"time":620824,"text":"that we described before."},{"time":622677,"text":"She puts out her hand.\nThe product jumps into it."},{"time":625221,"text":"Or she has to reach in and get it."},{"time":627426,"text":"She scans it and \nshe puts it in the bucket."},{"time":629871,"text":"And all of the rest of the technology\nis kind of behind the scenes."},{"time":633667,"text":"So she gets to now focus on the\npicking and packing portion of her job."},{"time":637528,"text":"Never has any idle time,\nnever has to leave her mat."},{"time":640802,"text":"And actually we think\nnot only a more productive"},{"time":644942,"text":"and more accurate\nway to fill orders."},{"time":648212,"text":"We think it's a more\nfulfilling way to fill orders."}]},{"cues":[{"time":651622,"text":"The reason we can say\nthat, though, is that workers"},{"time":654830,"text":"in a lot of these\nbuildings now compete"},{"time":656972,"text":"for the privilege of working\nin the Kiva zone that day."},{"time":660154,"text":"And sometimes we'll catch\nthem on testimonial videos"},{"time":662817,"text":"saying such things as,"},{"time":664934,"text":"they have more energy after the\nday to play with their grandchildren,"},{"time":669180,"text":"or in one case a guy said, \"the\nKiva zone is so stress-free"},{"time":673776,"text":"that I've actually stopped taking\nmy blood pressure medication.\""},{"time":676891,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":678725,"text":"That was at a pharmaceutical distributor,\nso they told us not to use that video."},{"time":682724,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":686292,"text":"So what I wanted to leave you\nwith today is the notion that"},{"time":689316,"text":"when you let things start\nto think and walk"},{"time":692171,"text":"and talk on their own, interesting\nprocesses and productivities can emerge."},{"time":697462,"text":"And now I think next time\nyou go to your front step"},{"time":700403,"text":"and pick up that box that\nyou just ordered online,"},{"time":702914,"text":"you break it open and\nthe goo is in there,"},{"time":705138,"text":"you'll have some wonderment\nas to whether a robot"},{"time":707891,"text":"assisted in the picking\nand packing of that order."}]},{"cues":[{"time":710484,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":712163,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}